OL,5,G2200 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,6,     FA crash leaves 29-year-old Ellie
OL,7,     Ftrapped in her car with critical
OL,8,     Finjuries. Meanwhile, 32-year-old
OL,9,     FClaire suffers a seizure at school
OL,10,     Fpickup, then seizes again en route
OL,11,     Fto hospital.
OL,12,G2300 Ambulance: Code Red
